%PDF-1.4
This is a deliberately minimal file for E2E testing: it passes PdfValidator's
mime-type + magic-byte check (starts with "%PDF-") but is not a structurally
valid PDF, so PdfTextExtractor (Apache PDFBox) fails to parse it and the
contract is correctly marked FAILED by ContractService — exercising the real
error-handling path end-to-end, consistent with the placeholder Anthropic key
used in this environment.
